News.headline: FA Youth Cup: Braintree Town v Dagenham and Redbridge
News.page_title: FA Youth Cup: Braintree Town v Dagenham and Redbridge
News.URL_keywords: FA Youth Cup: Braintree Town v Dagenham and Redbridge
News.short_description: The Daggers Academy are playing away at Braintree Town in the third qualifying round of the FA Youth Cup.
News.description:
The game will be played at the Cressing Road Stadium today with a 7:30pm kick off.

For any fans wishing to go to the game the address for the Braintree Town is Clockhouse Way, Braintree, Essex, CM7 3DE.

Ticket Prices:
Adults: £5.00
Concessions/Juniors: £2.00
